OL,3,CWhat you need to know as party leaders
OL,4,Cset to go head-to-head in live debate
OL,6,FOn Sunday 19 April, the leaders of
OL,7,FWales' six larger political parties
OL,8,Fwill be going head-to-head in ITV
OL,9,FCymru Wales' election special
OL,10,Fprogramme: 'Wales Decides 2026 - The
OL,11,FDebate'.
OL,13,FPresented by Adrian Masters, it will
OL,14,Fsee the leaders battling it out on a
OL,15,Flive broadcast in the Senedd, hoping
OL,16,Fto persuade the people of Wales to
OL,17,Fvote for them in the Senedd Election
OL,18,Fon Thursday 7 May.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G1/8
OL,2,W+.-'*%/"-$+,(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
