OL,3,CWhat you need to know as party leaders
OL,4,Cset to go head-to-head in live debate
OL,6,FWhen the election takes place on 7
OL,7,FMay, voters will also experience a new
OL,8,Fvoting system, which has been
OL,9,Fintroduced with the intention of
OL,10,Fdelivering a more proportionally
OL,11,Frepresentative outcome based on how
OL,12,Fpeople vote.
OL,14,FVoters will also be electing 96 Senedd
OL,15,FMembers to Cardiff Bay, an increase on
OL,16,Fthe 60 that there have been since
OL,17,Fdevolution began in 1999.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G3/8
