OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F462A1776363050
OL,3,CWhat you need to know as party leaders
OL,4,Cset to go head-to-head in live debate
OL,6,FThere is a difference in casting
OL,7,Fvotes. We will be given a single
OL,8,Fballot paper and asked to choose one
OL,9,Fparty or an independent candidate.
OL,11,FThose votes are then added up and
OL,12,Fdivided using a system known as the
OL,13,Fd'Hondt method to select six winners
OL,14,Fin each constituency.
OL,16,FOne effect of these changes will be
OL,17,Fthat it is extremely unlikely that any
OL,18,Fparty will win enough Senedd seats to
OL,19,Fform a government on its own.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G5/8
OL,2,W+.-'*%/"-$+,(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
