OL,3,CWhat you need to know as party leaders
OL,4,Cset to go head-to-head in live debate
OL,6,FDespite a drop in vote share to 33%,
OL,7,FPlaid Cymru is still on course to be
OL,8,Fthe largest party with a seat
OL,9,Fprojection suggesting it could win 43
OL,10,Fseats, leaving Rhun ap Iorwerth six
OL,11,Fshort of forming an overall majority
OL,12,Fin the Senedd.
OL,14,FMeanwhile Reform UK has closed the gap
OL,15,Fon Plaid after increasing its share to
OL,16,F27% since our last poll, which, in
OL,17,Fthis scenario, would translate to 30
OL,18,Fmembers of the Senedd.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G7/8
